
# Install

```shell
$ npm i autokill
```
## Example Code
```javascript
const client = new Discord.Client({intents: [Intents]})
const { AutoKill } = require('autokill')
AutoKill({Client: client, Time: 5000}) // Time Must be in Milliseconds And More Than 5 Seconds!
```
